_sText:
Short Bunny Hop map by me.

Once again I use flat textures because I am not skilled enough to make something look realistic, sorry for the people who do not enjoy this style, I sorta like it.

Thanks to mang-o for motivating me on finishing this map, this map is for him <3 I was going to call it bhop_mang-o but it honestly didn't suit it so here it is, bhop_backstreet. Simple map finished in under a week from a project I started a long time ago. Any feedback will be appreciated.

Enjoy
